The paper deals with control strategies for robots or automated systems, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of adaptive control and iterative learning control also suggests that the paper could be categorized under systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions transfer learning, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the experimental results involve quadrotors, which are often used in computer vision applications (cs.CV).
